{
  "stem": "6719.9",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have to deal with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, if you don't like it, just excuse yourself and walk out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it never happened before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I'm being asked about do you believe in God?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I say no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Especially in Roman Catholic schools.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I said, God went on a holiday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, how he let all these children die is beyond me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I cannot understand it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I said, I believe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said, but I don't know what to believe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But if you come straight out and say, do you believe in God?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I must say no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I believe in my heritage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I believe who I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But that's about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "How often do you speak in schools?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, maybe two-- twice a week, as often as I can.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I have to stay at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My wife is not well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we're getting nearer to the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I know it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we accept.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We accept.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's fait accompli.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's coming-- when, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The later the better, but not if you're not well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there's a lot of things that I laugh about it, and I make jokes about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You can always joke about yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we are now at an age where we have to think, hey, it's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- but I'm still-- I'm still in love with my wife.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm still in love with my daughter, and my sister, and my granddaughter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They're great.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- If that's the dividend that one reaps, or the-- then everybody should have-- should be as lucky as I am in that respect.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Life is beautiful when you have a family like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's, it's not always honey, and wine, and butter, and bread, and cake.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
